'''''You Are All Diseased''''' is the 16th album and 11th [[Home Box Office|HBO]] live broadcast stand-up special by comedian [[George Carlin]], recorded on February 6, 1999 at the [[Beacon Theatre (New York City)|Beacon Theater]] in [[New York, New York|New York City]] and released on CD in May of that year.
